        %h3{ id: 'user-groups' } User Groups
        %p You can use CKAN Groups to create and manage collections of datasets. This could be to catalogue datasets for a particular project or team, or collect data on a particular theme, or as a very simple way to help people find and search your own published datasets.

        %h4{ id: 'create-a-user-group' } Create a User Group

        %p Click the "add user group" button. The "Create User Group" page will load. Name your user group and add a description. Upload an image or link to be viewed on your user group page.

